ue\">QMS-P-005</div></div>\n                    <div class=\"cover-meta-card\"><div class=\"cover-meta-label\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-original-contenteditable=\"false\">版本 / 状态</div><div class=\"cover-meta-value\"><span contenteditable=\"true\" data-original-contenteditable=\"true\">01</span><span contenteditable=\"true\" class=\"text-emerald-600 text-[0.8rem] font-bold ml-2 bg-emerald-50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded border border-emerald-200 font-sans\" data-original-contenteditable=\"true\">现行有效</span></div></div>\n                    <div class=\"cover-meta-card\"><div class=\"cover-meta-label\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-original-contenteditable=\"false\">生效日期</div><div class=\"cover-meta-value font-mono\" contenteditable=\"true\" data-original-contenteditable=\"true\">2026-04-01</div></div>\n                    <div class=\"cover-meta-card\"><div class=\"cover-meta-label\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-original-contenteditable=\"false\">主导部门</div><div class=\"cover-meta-value font-sans\" contenteditable=\"true\" data-original-contenteditable=\"true\">供应链管理中心</div></div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- 第2页：修订履历 -->\n        <div class=\"a4-page\">\n            <table class=\"w-full border-0 print-table\" style=\"border:none !important;\">\n                <thead>\n                    <tr>\n                        <td class=\"pb-3 border-0\">\n                            <div class=\"page-header\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-original-contenteditable=\"false\">\n                                <span class=\"header-doc-no z-10 bg-white pr-2\" contenteditable=\"true\" data-original-contenteditable=\"true\">QMS-P-005</span>\n                                <span class=\"absolute left-0 right-0 text-center text-slate-400 font-sans z-0 whitespace-nowrap\" style=\"font-size: 7.5pt !important; letter-spacing: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"true\" data-original-contenteditable=\"true\">本文中的所有信息均为深圳市昊一源科技有限公司内部信息，不得向外传播</span>\n